race.comment: SWEET LOLLIPOP (8) took the sit on the lead but levelled up to score (24.06) at Rockhampton in a Grade 1/2 over 407m. Some good form is emerging from her last run. Looks the testing material. HARA'S NEO (5) has a terrific record this track and trip with four wins and one placing from five starts. Comes off a (21.52) win last time, scoring by 2.5 lengths in a OPEN over 390m at this track. Looks a key chance on best figures. KYOTO (4) jumped from out wide and was game in defeat last start when a neck second (19.84) behind Aussie Zip at Capalaba. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Bold showing expected. SHE'S A SHOWGIRL (1) will have admirers again after placing at this track and distance last time out.
